{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your role as a car carrier driver goes beyond just driving. You'll need to carefully load and unload vehicles, making sure each car is secured properly to avoid damage. Time management is key, as each job must be completed within a set timeframe, requiring precision and efficiency in handling the cars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286790/extras/CCS_1_gif-1.gif?t=1732023037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your success depends on how quickly, efficiently and without damage you can deliver the vehicles. The better you perform, the more money you\u2019ll earn, allowing you to grow your empire. You'll face challenges like changing weather conditions such as rain or snow, traffic jams, and other unpredictable situations. These obstacles will require careful planning in advance to ensure smooth deliveries and continued success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286790/extras/make-money.gif?t=1732023037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br>As you earn money for every job completed, you'll have the opportunity to grow your car transport business. Expand your fleet, hire employees, take on increasingly complex and lucrative missions. Managing your resources, making business decisions and upgrading your truck are essential parts of building your empire in the auto transport industry.  <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286790/extras/manage.gif?t=1732023037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you build a car transport empire and become the top carrier in the industry?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg